<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover" />
<title>ADHD 자가검사 · 성인 주의력 선별</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" crossorigin />
<link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin
  href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css" />
<style>
  :root{
    --paper:#F5F6F8;
    --card:#FFFFFF;
    --ink:#16181D;
    --ink-2:#3A3F49;
    --sub:#6A707C;
    --faint:#9AA0AB;
    --line:#E7E9ED;
    --line-2:#EFF1F4;
    --brand:#2B4C6F;
    --brand-soft:#EAF0F6;
    /* 중증도 (절제된 의미색) */
    --c-normal:#3F8F6B;
    --c-caution:#C0953A;
    --c-suspect:#C5743A;
    --c-moderate:#B05A3E;
    --c-severe:#A24249;
    --shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(20,24,33,.04), 0 8px 28px rgba(20,24,33,.06);
    --shadow-sm:0 1px 2px rgba(20,24,33,.05);
    --radius:18px;
    --mono:"SF Mono",ui-monospace,"Roboto Mono",Menlo,Consolas,monospace;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
  html,body{margin:0;padding:0}
  body{
    font-family:"Pretendard Variable",Pretendard,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,system-ui,sans-serif;
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    line-height:1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;
    letter-spacing:-.01em;
  }
  .wrap{max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 18px;padding-bottom:64px}
  .screen{display:none;animation:rise .5s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)}
  .screen.active{display:block}
  @keyframes rise{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
    .screen,.fill,*{animation:none!important;transition:none!important}
  }

  /* ── 상단 바 ── */
  .topbar{
    position:sticky;top:0;z-index:30;
    background:rgba(245,246,248,.82);
    backdrop-filter:saturate(180%) blur(18px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter:saturate(180%) blur(18px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-2);
  }
  .topbar-in{max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:13px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
  .brandmark{
    width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:8px;flex:0 0 auto;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),#3E6E94);
    display:grid;place-items:center;
  }
  .brandmark svg{width:15px;height:15px}
  .brandname{font-size:14.5px;font-weight:650;letter-spacing:-.02em}
  .brandname small{display:block;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:500;color:var(--faint);letter-spacing:.02em;margin-top:-1px}
  .topbar-spacer{flex:1}
  .iconbtn{
    border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--card);color:var(--sub);
    width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:10px;display:grid;place-items:center;cursor:pointer;
    transition:.15s;
  }
  .iconbtn:hover{color:var(--ink);border-color:#D7DAE0}
  .iconbtn svg{width:17px;height:17px}

  /* ── 히어로 ── */
  .hero{padding:38px 0 10px}
  .eyebrow{
    font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--brand);margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  h1.title{font-size:31px;line-height:1.18;font-weight:760;letter-spacing:-.035em;margin:0 0 14px}
  .lede{font-size:15px;color:var(--sub);margin:0 0 26px;max-width:440px}
  .lede b{color:var(--ink-2);font-weight:600}

  /* 스펙트럼 시그니처 */
  .spectrum{margin:26px 0 8px}
  .spectrum-bar{
    height:12px;border-radius:99px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--c-normal) 0%,var(--c-caution) 33%,var(--c-suspect) 58%,var(--c-moderate) 78%,var(--c-severe) 100%);
    position:relative;
  }
  .spectrum-bar.lg{height:16px}
  .spectrum-marker{
    position:absolute;top:50%;width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;
    background:#fff;border:3px solid var(--ink);transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
    box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.22);transition:left .9s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1);
  }
  .spectrum-labels{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:9px;font-size:11px;color:var(--faint);font-weight:500}

  /* ── 카드 ── */
  .card{
    background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);
    padding:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);margin:14px 0;
  }
  .card.flush{padding:0;overflow:hidden}
  .card-pad{padding:20px}

  /* ── 버튼 ── */
  .btn{
    width:100%;border:none;border-radius:14px;padding:16px;font-size:16px;font-weight:650;
    cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;letter-spacing:-.01em;transition:.18s;
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;
  }
  .btn-primary{background:var(--ink);color:#fff}
  .btn-primary:hover{background:#2A2E37}
  .btn-primary:active{transform:scale(.99)}
  .btn-ghost{background:var(--card);color:var(--ink);border:1px solid var(--line)}
  .btn-ghost:hover{border-color:#CFD3DA;background:#FAFBFC}
  .btn-soft{background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand)}
  .btn-soft:hover{background:#E0EAF3}
  .btn-row{display:flex;gap:10px}
  .btn-row .btn{flex:1}
  .btn-sm{padding:12px;font-size:14.5px;border-radius:12px}

  /* 입력 */
  .field{margin:18px 0 8px}
  .field label{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-2);margin-bottom:8px}
  .field input{
    width:100%;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:13px;padding:14px 15px;
    font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--ink);background:#FAFBFC;transition:.15s;letter-spacing:-.01em;
  }
  .field input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--brand);background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--brand-soft)}
  .field .hint{font-size:12px;color:var(--faint);margin-top:7px}

  /* 고지 */
  .notice{
    display:flex;gap:11px;background:#FBF8F0;border:1px solid #F0E6CF;border-radius:14px;
    padding:14px 15px;font-size:12.5px;color:#7A6630;line-height:1.55;
  }
  .notice svg{width:17px;height:17px;flex:0 0 auto;margin-top:1px}
  .notice b{font-weight:650;color:#5F4E1F}

  /* ── 검사 진행 ── */
  .progress{padding:24px 0 6px}
  .progress-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:11px}
  .progress-count{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--sub)}
  .progress-count b{color:var(--ink);font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
  .progress-part{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--brand);text-transform:uppercase}
  .track{height:5px;background:var(--line-2);border-radius:99px;overflow:hidden}
  .fill{height:100%;background:var(--ink);border-radius:99px;width:0;transition:width .45s cubic-bezier(.3,.8,.3,1)}

  .q-num{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--faint);font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:9px}
  .q-text{font-size:20px;font-weight:650;line-height:1.42;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin:0 0 4px;min-height:84px}
  .q-sub{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--faint);margin-bottom:20px}

  .opts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px}
  .opt{
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;width:100%;text-align:left;cursor:pointer;
    border:1.5px solid var(--line);background:var(--card);border-radius:14px;padding:15px 16px;
    font-family:inherit;font-size:15.5px;font-weight:550;color:var(--ink-2);transition:.14s;
  }
  .opt:hover{border-color:#C9CFD8;background:#FBFBFC}
  .opt .dot{
    width:21px;height:21px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--line);flex:0 0 auto;transition:.14s;position:relative;
  }
  .opt.sel{border-color:var(--brand);background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand)}
  .opt.sel .dot{border-color:var(--brand);background:var(--brand)}
  .opt.sel .dot::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:4px;background:#fff;border-radius:50%}
  .opt .scale{margin-left:auto;font-size:11px;color:var(--faint);font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;font-weight:600}

  .nav-row{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:22px}
  .nav-back{flex:0 0 auto;width:54px}

  /* ── 결과 ── */
  .result-hero{text-align:center;padding:30px 0 6px}
  .res-badge{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:7px 15px;border-radius:99px;
    font-size:13px;font-weight:650;margin-bottom:18px;letter-spacing:-.01em;
  }
  .res-name{display:none}
  .res-tier{font-size:33px;font-weight:780;letter-spacing:-.04em;margin:0 0 7px;line-height:1.1}
  .res-line{font-size:14.5px;color:var(--sub);max-width:420px;margin:0 auto}

  .score-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--line);border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;margin:6px 0}
  .score-cell{background:var(--card);padding:16px 12px;text-align:center}
  .score-cell .v{font-size:25px;font-weight:740;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;letter-spacing:-.03em}
  .score-cell .v span{font-size:13px;color:var(--faint);font-weight:600}
  .score-cell .k{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--sub);margin-top:3px;font-weight:550}

  .sect-label{font-size:12px;font-weight:680;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--faint);margin:0 0 14px}

  .subbar{margin:16px 0}
  .subbar-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:8px}
  .subbar-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:620}
  .subbar-name small{font-weight:500;color:var(--faint);font-size:11.5px;margin-left:5px}
  .subbar-val{font-size:13px;font-weight:680;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
  .subbar-track{height:9px;background:var(--line-2);border-radius:99px;overflow:hidden}
  .subbar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:99px;width:0;transition:width .8s cubic-bezier(.3,.8,.3,1)}

  .screener{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;padding:15px 16px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid var(--line)}
  .screener .pill{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:12px;flex:0 0 auto;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:740;font-size:17px;color:#fff;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
  .screener .txt{font-size:13px;line-height:1.5}
  .screener .txt b{font-weight:680;display:block;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px}

  .analysis p{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-2);margin:0 0 13px;line-height:1.62}
  .analysis p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
  .analysis b{font-weight:660;color:var(--ink)}
  .tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;margin:4px 0 16px}
  .tag{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:99px;background:#F1F3F6;color:var(--ink-2)}

  .rec-list{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0}
  .rec-list li{display:flex;gap:11px;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-2);padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-2);line-height:1.55}
  .rec-list li:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .rec-list .ic{flex:0 0 auto;width:19px;height:19px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand);display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;margin-top:1px}

  /* ── 표본/분포 ── */
  .dist-head{padding:30px 0 6px}
  .stat-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--line);border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;margin:14px 0}
  .stat-cell{background:var(--card);padding:17px 16px}
  .stat-cell .v{font-size:27px;font-weight:760;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;letter-spacing:-.03em}
  .stat-cell .v small{font-size:13px;color:var(--faint);font-weight:600}
  .stat-cell .k{font-size:12px;color:var(--sub);margin-top:2px}

  .distbar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin:13px 0}
  .distbar-label{flex:0 0 92px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
  .distbar-label .sw{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:3px;flex:0 0 auto}
  .distbar-track{flex:1;height:24px;background:var(--line-2);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;position:relative}
  .distbar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:8px;width:0;transition:width .7s cubic-bezier(.3,.8,.3,1);min-width:2px}
  .distbar-n{flex:0 0 auto;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:680;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;width:54px;text-align:right;color:var(--ink-2)}

  .member{
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;padding:13px 4px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-2);cursor:pointer;transition:.12s;
  }
  .member:hover{background:#FAFBFC;border-radius:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px}
  .member:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .member .av{
    width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:11px;flex:0 0 auto;display:grid;place-items:center;
    font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;
  }
  .member .info{flex:1;min-width:0}
  .member .nm{font-size:14.5px;font-weight:620;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
  .member .meta{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--faint);margin-top:1px}
  .member .tierbadge{font-size:11.5px;font-weight:680;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:8px;flex:0 0 auto}
  .member .sc{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;flex:0 0 auto;width:34px;text-align:right;color:var(--sub)}

  .empty{text-align:center;padding:44px 20px;color:var(--faint)}
  .empty svg{width:40px;height:40px;margin-bottom:14px;opacity:.5}
  .empty p{font-size:14px;margin:0}

  .mode-chip{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;
    padding:5px 11px;border-radius:99px;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--sub);background:var(--card);
  }
  .mode-chip .led{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%}
  .mode-chip.shared .led{background:var(--c-normal)}
  .mode-chip.local .led{background:var(--faint)}

  /* ── 모달 ── */
  .modal-bg{
    position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(22,24,29,.46);z-index:60;display:none;
    align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center;backdrop-filter:blur(3px);
  }
  .modal-bg.open{display:flex;animation:fade .25s ease}
  @keyframes fade{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
  .modal{
    background:var(--card);width:100%;max-width:560px;border-radius:24px 24px 0 0;
    padding:22px 20px calc(24px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));max-height:88vh;overflow-y:auto;
    animation:slideup .32s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1);
  }
  @keyframes slideup{from{transform:translateY(100%)}to{transform:none}}
  @media(min-width:600px){
    .modal-bg{align-items:center}
    .modal{border-radius:22px;max-height:84vh;animation:fade .2s ease}
  }
  .modal-grip{width:38px;height:4px;border-radius:99px;background:var(--line);margin:0 auto 16px}
  .modal h3{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 4px;letter-spacing:-.02em}
  .modal .msub{font-size:13px;color:var(--sub);margin:0 0 18px}
  .modal-steps{counter-reset:s;list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0 0 18px}
  .modal-steps li{position:relative;padding:0 0 14px 32px;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.55}
  .modal-steps li::before{
    counter-increment:s;content:counter(s);position:absolute;left:0;top:0;
    width:21px;height:21px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--brand-soft);color:var(--brand);
    font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;display:grid;place-items:center;
  }
  .modal-steps code{background:#F1F3F6;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:5px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--brand)}

  .foot{text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:var(--faint);margin-top:34px;line-height:1.7}
  .foot a{color:var(--sub);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px dotted var(--line)}
  .divider{height:1px;background:var(--line-2);margin:22px 0}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-in">
    <div class="brandmark" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M4 13c2.5-6 5-6 7.5 0s5 6 7.5-2" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="brandname">주의력 자가검사<small>Adult ADHD · ASRS-v1.1</small></div>
    <div class="topbar-spacer"></div>
    <button class="iconbtn" id="navDist" title="표본 보기" aria-label="표본 보기">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M4 19V10M10 19V5M16 19v-6M22 19v-9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
    </button>
    <button class="iconbtn" id="navSet" title="설정" aria-label="설정">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 15a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M19.4 13a1.6 1.6 0 00.3 1.8l.1.1a2 2 0 11-2.8 2.8l-.1-.1a1.6 1.6 0 00-2.7 1.1V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.1A1.6 1.6 0 005 17.7l-.1.1a2 2 0 11-2.8-2.8l.1-.1A1.6 1.6 0 002.3 12H2a2 2 0 110-4h.1A1.6 1.6 0 003.6 5.3l-.1-.1A2 2 0 116.3 2.4l.1.1A1.6 1.6 0 009 1.4V1a2 2 0 114 0v.1a1.6 1.6 0 002.7 1.1l.1-.1a2 2 0 112.8 2.8l-.1.1a1.6 1.6 0 001.1 2.7H22a2 2 0 110 4h-.1a1.6 1.6 0 00-1.5 1z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" transform="scale(.82) translate(2.6 2.6)"/></svg>
    </button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">

  <!-- ════════ 시작 화면 ════════ -->
  <section class="screen active" id="screen-home">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">성인 주의력 선별검사</div>
      <h1 class="title">혹시 나도 ADHD일까?<br/>18문항으로 확인해 보세요.</h1>
      <p class="lede">세계보건기구(WHO)가 개발하고 정신과 진료 현장에서 쓰이는 <b>성인 ADHD 자가보고 척도(ASRS-v1.1)</b>를 그대로 사용합니다. 약 2분이면 끝나며, 결과는 <b>주의력결핍·과잉행동/충동</b> 두 축으로 분석해 드립니다.</p>

      <div class="spectrum">
        <div class="spectrum-bar"></div>
        <div class="spectrum-labels"><span>정상</span><span>주의</span><span>의심</span><span>중등도</span><span>중증</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="field" style="margin-top:4px">
        <label for="nick">닉네임</label>
        <input id="nick" type="text" maxlength="14" placeholder="단톡방에서 쓰는 이름" autocomplete="off" />
        <div class="hint">표본(분포)에 이 이름으로 결과가 기록돼요. 같은 이름으로 다시 하면 최신 결과로 갱신됩니다.</div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" id="startBtn" style="margin-top:6px">검사 시작하기</button>
      <button class="btn btn-soft btn-sm" id="seeDist" style="margin-top:9px">먼저 단톡방 표본부터 보기</button>
    </div>

    <div class="notice">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 9v4M12 17h.01M10.3 3.9 2.4 18a2 2 0 001.7 3h15.8a2 2 0 001.7-3L13.7 3.9a2 2 0 00-3.4 0z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      <div><b>이 검사는 진단이 아닙니다.</b> 선별(screening) 도구로, ADHD 가능성을 살펴보는 참고용입니다. 정확한 진단은 정신건강의학과 전문의의 면담과 평가를 통해서만 가능합니다.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="foot">
      ASRS-v1.1 · WHO Composite International Diagnostic Interview 기반<br/>
      <a id="aboutLink">검사·채점 방식 안내</a>
